{"tha-ap454:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap454:0.2":"Jagatidayakavagga ","tha-ap454:0.3":"Morahatthiyattheraapadana ","tha-ap454:1.1":"“Morahattham gahetvana, ","tha-ap454:1.2":"upesim lokanayakam; ","tha-ap454:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap454:1.4":"morahatthamadasaham. ","tha-ap454:2.1":"Imina morahatthena, ","tha-ap454:2.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap454:2.3":"Nibbayimsu tayo aggi, ","tha-ap454:2.4":"labhami vipulam sukham. ","tha-ap454:3.1":"Aho buddha aho dhamma, ","tha-ap454:3.2":"aho no satthusampada; ","tha-ap454:3.3":"Datvanaham morahattham, ","tha-ap454:3.4":"labhami vipulam sukham. ","tha-ap454:4.1":"Tiyaggi nibbuta mayham, ","tha-ap454:4.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap454:4.3":"Sabbasava parikkhina, ","tha-ap454:4.4":"natthi dani punabbhavo. ","tha-ap454:5.1":"Ekatimse ito kappe, ","tha-ap454:5.2":"yam danamadadim tada; ","tha-ap454:5.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap454:5.4":"morahatthassidam phalam. ","tha-ap454:6.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap454:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap454:6.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap454:7.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap454:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap454:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap454:8.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap454:8.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap454:8.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap454:9.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma morahatthiyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap454:10.1":"Morahatthiyattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}